<!DOCTYPE html>
<html> 
    <body>
        <div id="div1">
        <h1>ðŸ’žShipping Scenario GeneratorðŸ’ž</h1>
        <h6>Created by <a href="https://instagram.com/grazgrain" style="color: silver;">grazgrain</a></h6>
        <input type="text" id="A" placeholder="Person A"></input>
        <br>
        <input type="text" id="B" placeholder="Person B"></input>
        <br>
        <br>
        <button id="generator" onclick="generate()">Generate!</button>
        </div>
        <div id="div2"><p id='generatedText'></p></div>
       
        
    </body> 

    <script>
            let personA = ""; 
            let personB = ""; 
    document
        .getElementById("A")
        .addEventListener('input', (event) => {
            personA = event.target.value;
        });

    document
        .getElementById("B")
        .addEventListener('input', (event) => {
            personB = event.target.value;
        });

        
        function generate(){
            const scenarios = [
            `${personA} and ${personB} in the Wild West. ${personA} is an outlaw while ${personB} is a sheriff.`, 
            `${personA} asks ${personB} if they would still love them if they were a worm. If you want to take it a step further, have ${personA} actually turn into a worm.`, 
            `${personA} and ${personB}'s third wheel describes the couple's relationship.`,
            `${personA} and ${personB} have to babysit and have to figure out how to take care of a child. Chaos ensues.`, 
            `${personA} and ${personB} are at this point just friends. ${personB} is playing spin the bottle and it keeps landing on ${personA}.`, 
            `${personA} falls into ${personB}'s arms while rollerskating.`,
            `${personA} is a barista and ${personB} is their customer. They both have crushes on each other but neither know how to confess their love.`,
            `${personB} is a celebrity and ${personA} is a big fan of them. One day, they meet each other, and one thing leads to another and they start dating. Drama and gossip ensues.`,
            `If ${personA} and ${personB} ruled a country, what would it be like?`,
            `${personA} and ${personB}'s first kiss.`,
            `${personA} and ${personB} are just like that couple from Titanic (only no one dies). Oh my god you guys!`,
            `${personA} and ${personB} make playlists for each other.`,
            `${personA} and ${personB} are about to get married, when suddenly another character yells "I object!"`,
            `${personA} and ${personB} very awkwardly meet each other's parents.`, 
            `${personA} and ${personB} troll people online together. It goes very wrong.`,
            `${personA} and ${personB} get in one of those weird slapstick fights Tom and Jerry type fights where there's pianos falling from the sky and stuff.`,
            `${personA} and ${personB} cry to each other both for completely different reasons and try to comfort the other but can't because they're crying and sniffling so much.`,
            `A true crime documentary about ${personA} and ${personB}, partners in crime`,
            `${personA} and ${personB} get lost in New York City together and don't find their friends until the end of the story.`,
            `${personA} and ${personB} switch bodies like in Freaky Friday.`,
            `${personA} was a punk, ${personB} did ballet. What more can I say?`,
            `Scott Pilgrim AU where ${personA} is Scott and ${personB} is Ramona. Who are ${personB}'s seven evil exes?`
        ];
            let genScen = scenarios[Math.floor(Math.random() * scenarios.length)]; 
            document.getElementById('generatedText').innerHTML = genScen; 

            if (personB == "" || personA == "") {
                document.getElementById('generatedText').innerHTML = "Please enter both names before generating!"; 
            }
        }
        </script>

